{"tid":1917514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世良言】一齊改變自己，拯救連登","createTime":"2020-03-09T13:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T09:03:59.000Z","uid":126626,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"730ecad46a7762942b550c865c40f234ed9d5385","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:51:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">篇文唔係我寫，係網上一個專家講文宣戰。<br />\n連登有咁多網軍同五毛，連登仔成日話要踢走大台，我哋都要自律，睇下傳媒人點講。<br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推呢個正經post，唔該大家！<br />\n<br />\ncredit: terry的媒體懶人堂</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpUDx6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpUDx6s.jpg&h=89ce21ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【媒體攻略】團結才是最好的文宣<br />\n<br />\n這兩天，政府已高聲宣布：從來沒有靜。<br />\n<br />\n落地難打，就做文宣。而文宣最大的威力，是團結。 <br />\n<br />\n我們不改習慣，這場仗會很難打。<br />\n<br />\n這九個月，做媒體分析，得出一個結論：<br />\n<br />\n黃營做文宣愈來愈難，藍營則愈來愈容易。<br />\n<br />\n幾分鐘，講講媒體戰。<br />\n<br />\n【環境作用】<br />\n資訊戰爭裡，社會撕裂，絕對是好事。<br />\n<br />\n因為兩邊愈對立，文宣愈易做。<br />\n<br />\n正因為沒有中間派，所以黃藍打文宣戰，某程度上都是立場主導。<br />\n<br />\n而對家愈有問題，己方就愈團結。於是，只要鬧政府和警察，就算是假新聞，黃絲都照信無誤。<br />\n<br />\n同樣，但凡指責示威者的，如像爆眼少女是被黃絲誤中之流的假資訊，一樣可以瘋傳。<br />\n<br />\n當立場先於事實，目標就很重要。這種環境作用，沒有好與壞，只講求你的目極。<br />\n<br />\n你要求真，還是求快感？<br />\n<br />\n【黃營的困局】<br />\n<br />\n首先，黃藍是極度簡化的概念。會如此演變，正因為去年六月訂下的原則：不分不割。<br />\n<br />\n所以，不論派別、不論光譜，和政權對立的，都是自己人。<br />\n<br />\n去大台，沒有政治老人打擾，才能走到今天。但本質上，我們有各自思想，要得出共識，需要時間。<br />\n<br />\n例如近期，要不要打功能組別，至今都沒有共識。<br />\n<br />\n假設我們達成結論，要主力選戰；藍營馬上就有共識：恥笑黃絲玩選舉。<br />\n<br />\n黃營需要大量時間與討論，也不確定有成效，甚至在過程同已亂了軍心。但藍營只需反對我們贊成的，已經可以上下一心，反應迅速。<br />\n<br />\n這並非二元投票。人多，也有其煩惱。<br />\n<br />\n【演算法與同溫層】<br />\n<br />\n我們在社交媒體看到的，都是各自的「主流民意」。<br />\n<br />\n正如區選前，藍絲會自認沉默的大多數，因為他們現實和網上見的，都是反暴徒反暴力。<br />\n<br />\n黃絲都一樣，我們見親友與網民一律反警暴，都覺得民情是壓倒性。<br />\n<br />\n這種現象，基於講到牙都甩的演算法（Algorithm）。<br />\n<br />\n你會看到《立場》，朋友們都在分享《蘋果》，圖與片九成是反暴政。背後是演算法排的話劇，你喜歡什麼，就給你看什麼。<br />\n<br />\n你愈喜歡，同溫層就愈穩固。<br />\n<br />\n如上段所言，黃絲在同溫層內要達成結論極其困難。因為光復香港，可不是一兩個決定就成事。<br />\n<br />\n問題來了，同溫層裡無法避免的消耗，我們可以怎樣做？<br />\n<br />\n【自我約束，建立習慣】<br />\n<br />\n看看FB的黃絲大群絲，也望望連登的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n不論任何時期，話題分支甚多。情緒作用，不斷有假新聞與狙擊Post，大多數無關宏旨。<br />\n<br />\n兩日前，清算與疫情仍然肆虐，但其一主流議題，是中學YouTuber雞丁。<br />\n<br />\n藍定黃，打定放？佔據的時間與互動量多得驚人。<br />\n<br />\n是否不能討論？香港是自由社會，什麼都可以講。<br />\n<br />\n但若然咩都講一餐，所謂民意的壓力，又有何意義？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">回望醫護罷工，到第三日，全城熱話是搶廁紙。<br />\n<br />\n重要嗎？或者重要，但怎樣都及不上講罷工。<br />\n<br />\n幾日後，醫護工業行動悄然落幕了。當晚居然有不少熱門，在心譴責工會力度不足。<br />\n<br />\n又試問，我們這些外部人士，是否就出盡了力？<br />\n<br />\n沒有良好的習慣，民意就會打散。再多的悲劇與核彈，都是徒然。</span><br />\n<br />\n連登與IG上的網軍，都是以消耗戰為主。不斷開搶眼的話題引爆討論，或者挑起政治罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n九個月了，抗爭心神已日減。無聊事講了幾個鐘，就這麼，光復就變了次要。<br />\n<br />\n文宣戰，最可怕是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n回想吧，721與831。輿論力量之大，在於是話題集中，也就是團結。<br />\n<br />\n【無需大台，但要主題】<br />\n<br />\n團結，要統籌戰線。其實也不需要大台，我們自律就夠。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼不斷有前高官出來講，某某親戚個朋友個女個中學同學，是免費黃絲天使。<br />\n<br />\n一來，藍營會信。<br />\n二來，黃營會講。<br />\n<br />\n兩樣中一樣已經贏，與搶廁紙事件同理，是如此簡單。<br />\n<br />\n所以我們需要主題。<br />\n<br />\n例如，這兩日的圍捕事件，警暴是主題，就要避免再討論雞丁小朋友。<br />\n<br />\n怎樣得出何謂主題？過程一定有討論，但這個過程，比分散話題實際得多。<br />\n<br />\n【我們可以做什麼？】<br />\n<br />\n早前跟大家討論過，在媒體戰爭之中，自我檢討的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n在此與各位重溫：<br />\n<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n1. 新聞類，不是正統媒體，盡量不轉發。<br />\n2. 未經Fact Check的消息，不要理。<br />\n3. 只轉發原創者的內容，養大同路人原創者<br />\n4. 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，鼓勵點擊原創平台。<br />\n<br />\n而目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n<br />\n比方說，<br />\n1. 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動Post；<br />\n2. 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3. 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4. 戒除政治J女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5. 未能Fact Check的事情，忍痛讓佢沉。<br />\n6. 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7. 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題<br />\n<br />\n議題熱度，講求集中。<br />\n輿論誠信，講求實例。<br />\n<br />\n【結論】<br />\n黃絲的困局，是壞習慣，也是自己。<br />\n<br />\n敵人是如此強橫，夢想是如此壯大，今天的路行不通，就要改變自我。<br />\n<br />\n沒有大台，沒有號令。我們在各自爬山的路徑，方向至少要一致。<br />\n<br />\n改變世界之前，先改善自己。也正因為我們懂得反省，才沒有淪為藍絲。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，撐住，共勉之。<br />\n/<br />\n請Like Terry的媒體懶人堂<br />\n一日一篇，看時事，看媒體。<br />\nIG：Terry_yeung_blog<br />\nIG連結：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IMS6HI&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=39fab00f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IMS6HI</a><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/198069921605920/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108102623935984%2Fposts%2F198069921605920%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=123f07f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108102623935984/posts/198069921605920/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"23b68a36f73e6b80d8433fb8312897cd7cd9a821","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:52:16.000Z","msg":"正經post好難推，要大家一齊俾啲掙扎"},{"pid":"21fb11eb53d2a860a7dccb1eef842716517eb133","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"我認我on9，有份推on9講車震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲真心易做好多，黃絲成日內鬥，真速要急起直追"},{"pid":"040f27dbebf8f9538af257e182aed92d220002b7","tid":1917514,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0986ff5bdb5704a1efdc6449b9ab241c0ba4b518","tid":1917514,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21fb11eb53d2a860a7dccb1eef842716517eb133","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"我認我on9，有份推on9講車震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲真心易做好多，黃絲成日內鬥，真速要急起直追"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"要認清目標"},{"pid":"842b3e5c3a61fe2c031345b88e3a5496c207a21e","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"呢單黑警逼人講對唔住又係on L 9，唔知手足而家點，見晒樣，尋到人未&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/147321776746495/?vh=e&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112467260231947%2Fposts%2F147321776746495%2F%3Fvh%3De%26d%3Dn&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FMwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=4bc59243\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112467260231947/posts/147321776746495/?vh=e&amp;d=n</a>"},{"pid":"401d4c82e1374aebd82474ac286170d72a08e27e","tid":1917514,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:56:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9a3c55218b64d2209e26acc2af7ced43300dd38","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"到底點樣建立共識？<br />\n<br />\n我哋係咪要定期投下票？<br />\n怕唔怕網軍洗票？"},{"pid":"3acfa94a75f0dfec6a19927b897e60671a3fe4c3","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:59:37.000Z","msg":"唔該大家幫我頂上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eb8ed8beee6802ebf1b14c3699ddb097229da3","tid":1917514,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"353280be0ef6ad5843007cb57e369913ae5645c7","tid":1917514,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3378d14a8f04fb1721f6b5c116f5ba5d4a3a09c1","tid":1917514,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:03:07.000Z","msg":"呢個重要<br />\n呢個就係一份報紙總編每日要做咩故仔，咩故要放頭版一樣道理<br />\n導火新聞線係好教材"},{"pid":"ebd1bed682bf29cdf3db08dfced7abd7db50387c","tid":1917514,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2cdd15d14ef06e5260318a653862edacd03b22","tid":1917514,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21fb11eb53d2a860a7dccb1eef842716517eb133","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"我認我on9，有份推on9講車震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n藍絲真心易做好多，黃絲成日內鬥，真速要急起直追"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"反擊比防守更容易"},{"pid":"bf1f11206160d2f29302800dc11e9d18bb5c3285","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:05:17.000Z","msg":"利申，可以當我打手<br />\n<br />\n但我覺得ter sir寫媒體野真心值得推，算係好理性分析。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我覺得佢上年上返水之後，變到有啲軟弱，比黃衛兵屌竟然道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可能做咗大粒就開始怕事，有啲失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下正經文推唔推到啦，同埋都credit番"},{"pid":"3294f2806d17662c848ad95ce3b3f1121af64d5d","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:06:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77d4e150e3f2560c39709a69904b5d07b08c57a6","tid":1917514,"uid":312513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:06:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e90253e74a5883cad3fe241bf2bb6cb46316b3b2","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:06:58.000Z","msg":"大家覺得今日最大核彈係咩？"},{"pid":"f8988fcbe2cd9794bc31f6cfbd5a6ba0372378d3","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:08:29.000Z","msg":"另外我覺得''作者''寫啲文都好正，''書生百用''都寫得好好"},{"pid":"f90c18ce20e7b5d502b81e1b1557b2d81bde7081","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:08:56.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"acd0dba996daffc40f5f8ca92f9dfd84d2cb05c8","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"Rui"},{"pid":"0e0244caba023d4c52e0ff28ca6d4347a6873cff","tid":1917514,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:10:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a935f6179d39e9f3cda7d9700ce6331a61092380","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"Rui"},{"pid":"a3df3a47b95c608d03a2df1543a9016b6a65b6ac","tid":1917514,"uid":315523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2djTm9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2djTm9P.jpg&h=28e3a449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OBHYygu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBHYygu.jpg&h=7c302c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0p2Yygw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0p2Yygw.jpg&h=2bb61d64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9a9da9a9dd10593dd1098eba2d15eb4642116eaa","tid":1917514,"uid":126626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T14:28:37.000Z","msg":"Rui"}]}